{"tid":1780042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期五晚七點半：旺角和你寫","createTime":"2019-12-12T05:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T04:12:10.000Z","uid":1435,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"15c4d28aa0cd5308209ad33b478532f631196ffe","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oh3W8xF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOh3W8xF.jpg&h=fbfcbad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n🎄🎄🎄 聖誕旺角和你寫 🎄🎄🎄<br />\n🎄🎄🎄 #一人一信  #送暖給手足 🎄🎄🎄<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月13日（五）<br />\n時間：7:30pm - 10:30pm<br />\n地點：旺角東行人天橋轉角<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動從6月至今，已超過70位手足還押，部分更需要一直還押至下年新年，無法與家人共渡聖誕。<br />\n<br />\n沒有願意奉獻自己的他們，反送中運動也必不可能堅持至今。當我們能在外自由地享受聖誕假期、消費、享樂，與家人朋友相聚，但那些手足只能孤獨地囚禁在收押所，等待面對漫長的訴訟、刑期，還有未知的人生前途。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們的文字便顯得重要，「義士不是condom」。透過聖誕卡、書信，讓還押的手足知道，他們並不孤單。我們也沒有忘記他們任何一位。<br />\n<br />\n🎄🎄🎄 活動詳情 🎄🎄🎄<br />\n<br />\n歡迎市民將寫好的信或聖誕卡交到街站（請參閱以下寫信須知，確保信件合乎標準，以免信件被DQ），義工將會一併收集及整理後轉交「被捕人士關注組」。<br />\n<br />\n現場亦會提供教學及少量信封、信紙及郵票，等市民可以即場寫信畀手足。<br />\n<br />\n🎄🎄🎄 寫信須知 🎄🎄🎄<br />\n<br />\n【寫的信會交到甚麼人手上？】<br />\n<br />\n如果有指定對象（例如：梁天琦、初一義士盧建民、袁智駒、容偉業（美國隊長）、連潤發（發仔）、佔中案陳健民教授），你可以在信紙上註明收信人全名，以茲識別。沒有指定對象的信件將隨機送到還押手足手上。<br />\n<br />\n【我們可以寫些什麼？】<br />\n<br />\n你可以寫任何東西給他們（除了逃獄、色情、人身攻擊和粗口、仔細描述監內情況的內容），譬如你想跟他們說的關心話、沒有忘記他們、支持他們、煲底相見、描述這陣子香港發生什麼事、你的感受和想法是什麼等等，什麼都可以的。最怕的不是你寫什麼，而是你什麼都不寫。<br />\n<br />\n留意為確保信件符合要求及保護收信手足，所有信件都會由義工先行閱覽才會送交到手足手上，義工小組承諾絕對不會外洩任何私隱。<br />\n<br />\n【寫信基本要求】<br />\n<br />\n1. 聖誕卡可購買現成、自行繪畫或設計印製；<br />\n2. 不可有任何附貼物，如絲帶、喱士、閃粉、貼紙等；<br />\n3. 不可有額外裝置，如音樂裝罝、彈弓裝置、閃燈裝置等；<br />\n4. 不可是立體設計、迷你咭，摺紙、有夾層 (即兩層紙黐埋一層)；<br />\n5. 不可用塗改液；<br />\n6. 尺寸不可大於 A4；<br />\n7. 不可寄書籍、郵票、回郵信封、書籤、咭片、日曆、含有賠率的體育新聞、貼上郵票和貼紙的紙；<br />\n8. 如使用信紙，信紙不一定是白色，但請盡量選素色信紙<br />\n9. 信內請勿包含色情，人身攻擊內容及粗言穢語；<br />\n10. 信件內可包括打印的圖片/照片，如屬相片則不可是在囚者的個人獨照，必須有其他人。由於每月收取相片數量有限，請將相片一同列印在信紙上，而並非沖哂出來的相片；<br />\n11. 信上不可貼上貼紙；<br />\n12. 如欲收到他們的回信，請在信內寫上回郵地址及姓名；<br />\n13. 因版權問題，請勿直接列印書籍內容；<br />\n14. 如果信件因格式或內容問題而未能寄出，將會保留直至他們重獲自由，然後親手遞交。"},{"pid":"2dd507ba435082f8d343fd9da294f2ce20feb611","tid":1780042,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972df9f8dc842697fe4a425919fa11f70c23a66c","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"旺角東連儂橋Telegram Channel<br />\n<br />\n旺角連儂橋影像紀錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mklennonbridge\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmklennonbridge&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=41d5ff56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mklennonbridge</a>"},{"pid":"72332a2f2471fbd63f054e8b4d4220bab287b729","tid":1780042,"uid":69515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"6773640f5fe01c8fb9417fe5751eb1df9462d8bf","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d97a464fff409c9a437c54e13880f270e20321f","tid":1780042,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"喂！！！！！<br />\n一陣就係啦<br />\n成班人淨係識講person of the year<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推下行動post啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n今日有612半週年集會  熱門一個post都冇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1780006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1780006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LrRc03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LrRc03.jpg&h=d69dc33b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">12/12/2019(四)<br />\n612半週年紀念 齊上齊落 集會<br />\n(*待批不反對通知書）<br />\n時間︰19:00 - 21:00<br />\n地點︰中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦︰民間集會團隊</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/CivilAssemblyTeam/764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilAssemblyTeam%2F764&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=6b430166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilAssemblyTeam/764</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=4719e3da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=03bb11fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=cfa5a139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a>"},{"pid":"a0e8232b58ddc7eebddb97d56417d47c8dcdb01a","tid":1780042,"uid":213163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"行動po推"},{"pid":"5f8cb0b77b219446e45b8f3f16859235f88b97ec","tid":1780042,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"純粹入嚟提醒一下<br />\n<br />\n旺角每晚都有手足比便衣狗拉，依家旺角係佢多便衣狗<br />\n<br />\n小部隊式係大馬路快閃唔再可行<br />\n<br />\n根本短期內就<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該再喺旺角快閃</span><br />\n依家啲狗轉晒策略，多咗好多便衣狗丶一見到有手足聚集就call台，搵狗車喺附近埋伏<br />\n但係我哋仲同以前一樣毫無進步<br />\n<br />\n而家佢係啲熱門地方派便衣狗，你少人快閃嘅話即刻拉<br />\n<br />\n解決方法有兩個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1 唔好再喺過往兩個月玩到熟曬嘅地方快閃堵路，有便衣狗監視<br />\n<br />\n2 人越多便衣狗越難行動，另外因為越來越多車巡，亦要多啲哨兵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f7a166e09b65bf54b8135d3e093b62afed23ea80","tid":1780042,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8098cb7699fac7952c801c1147760b588bba4875","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b35e408ddcf8987a3024c493a576900d342e883","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc6327834fb75cd2c7ac5ff694ebe838b1276c2","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd5ccb9b33f89f1e3973897c3eca0ad4d659ec0","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751af2ffad9ff037a82d655175462837238ecce1","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e584a933a0a4e4ffe38e1294e159f2958208d6dc","tid":1780042,"uid":324225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f90fa3edf4143845352d95e332d1e81ea5cc2e4","tid":1780042,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"希望大家寫下信比佢地"},{"pid":"b77c77f5f0d97896f4b7725071b1804aaddaa767","tid":1780042,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59542caa44804ea7f73b29b47f422eb60a38002f","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee0b43347dbec046907e780e1368da96e2b7361","tid":1780042,"uid":265969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"自備聖誕咭？"},{"pid":"8f3e57cd2b625e8a965fc9c397b39083bb95a381","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee0b43347dbec046907e780e1368da96e2b7361","tid":1780042,"uid":265969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"自備聖誕咭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"現場會有少量提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e813da0f58f39a38ff015545945e3ee4968bf52","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3699469e23a518df14e6041f68c96bc427d7b3ec","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d93079e795ba7b4f6f59b51eb10557527feb888","tid":1780042,"uid":1435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T00:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a2cd0d9a7cb59fed9ea5b3d57e5f20b7320d47","tid":1780042,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T00:26:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5da72ec1be8d36e651b3ef54d9ac7f2464b4ef0","tid":1780042,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T00:27:43.000Z","msg":"尋晚都有人搞，已經寫左，大家俾啲暖氣俾在冷窗下的手足支持下佢地"}]}